建設及環境學院專注於研究[[可持續發展|可持續發展]]、[[智慧城市|智慧城市]]以及[[環境保護|環境保護]]工程。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education/article/2179100/time-invest-sustainable-future|title=Time to invest in a sustainable future|author=May Chan Rhodes|date=2019-01-08|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|accessdate=2021-03-13|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107235537/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education/article/2179100/time-invest-sustainable-future|dead-url=no}}</ref>

